    Pubs In Newcastle upon Tyne - The Five Swans - J D Wetherspoon

    https://www.jdwetherspoon.com/pubs/all-pubs/.../the-five-swans-newcastle-upon-tyne
    1. Cached
    2. Similar
    The Five Swans is a Wetherspoon pub in Newcastle upon Tyne, Tyne and Wear. Our pub offers a range of real ales, craft beers and freshly ground Lavazza coffee. Breakfast is served until noon, with our full food menu available until 11pm.
